/**
 * DeFi widget domain types — aligned with backend (UAC + execution-service).
 *
 * SSOT for enums/venues/instruments: lib/registry/ui-reference-data.json
 * (generated by unified-trading-pm/scripts/openapi/generate-unified-openapi.sh)
 *
 * The constants below are convenience copies for TypeScript type safety.
 * They MUST stay in sync with ui-reference-data.json. Run the OpenAPI sync
 * script after backend changes to regenerate.
 *
 * Mock-backed until API wiring. All IDs, enums, and field names match the
 * real backend so switching from mock → API is a data-source swap, not a rewrite.
 */

